Here's how to solve the issue with comdlg32.ocx

1. Check your WINDOWS/SYSTEM32 directory. If the file's missing, simply fetch it from somewhere and put it in here - then run the crack again (I myself were actually able to find it on my HD, but in another directory).

2. If the file is already there, try and register it manually to get it working: go to START -> Run and enter this command in the dialog box:

regsvr32 comdlg32.ocx
